data.description: WELCOME HOME~~You must see this gorgeous split floor plan, 4 bedroom home on a corner lot in the beautiful community of St. Andrews.   This amazing 4 sides brick home has a remodeled kitchen with modern granite countertops, updated appliances with gas available, and  touch activated kitchen faucet.  There is a breakfast bar, breakfast nook and formal dining room.   You will find updated tile in the kitchen and wood flooring in the family room as well as a vent free gas log fireplace.   The light fixtures have been upgraded throughout.  The bathrooms have  been recently updated with marble countertops, brushed nickel fixtures, tile shower and glass door.  There are in wall surround sound speakers, in wall safe and beautiful crown moulding.  The front door is an updated fiberglass door.  Out back you will find a nice screened porch, covered patio and a deck that on looks the beautifully landscaped yard. There are also raised garden beds with automatic drip irrigation.  This home is a re build Northwest FL participant with fabric-shield hurricane shutters, new garage door, additional roof straps, and impact rated glass patio door.  The garage is a spacious 2 car garage and has upgraded floor coating.  The neighborhood amenities include a park and picnic area. This home is a must see!! Call today for your private showing.
